      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Urban farmers, home gardeners, and commercial growers in Malaysia are increasingly using greenhouses and propagation tunnels for year-round cultivation. Maintaining optimal growing temperatures in tropical climates presents challenges. Bubble wrap offers an affordable, accessible insulation solution that improves plant growth while reducing energy costs for heating and cooling systems.</p>
