        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Place propagation trays on bubble wrap-covered surfaces to insulate from cold floors. Wrap around seedling trays to create mini-greenhouses that maintain consistent soil temperature for faster germination. Ideal for tropical year-round seed starting.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Creating Propagation Tunnels with Bubble Wrap</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Build low tunnels over seedling rows using PVC pipes and secured bubble wrap. This creates humid, warm microclimates that accelerate seedling growth. Easy to remove for watering and pest management.</p>

