        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Seedlings of peppers, tomatoes, and tropical vegetables are sensitive to temperature fluctuations. Bubble wrap protection maintains stable conditions, reducing transplant shock and improving survival rates in Malaysian growing seasons.</p>
